PrecisEnactment of an ORDER PROHIBITING ENTRY ON CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (2001, No. 07, CARCROSS/TAGISH FIRST NATION, Y.T.) - which (a) prohibits the staking of mineral claims or prospecting in specific areas in the Yukon until December 31, 2006, and (b) repeals the Prohibition of Entry on Certain Lands Order, No. 5 of 1996.
